<div class="legal">
	<div>
		This site uses different cookies and similar technologies, in three categories, each treated differently under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):
	</div>

	<section>
		<h2>Session cookie</h2>
		<div class="text text-justify">
			A technical cookie, strictly necessary for the site to work (navigation, staying logged in), is set automatically. Under the applicable regulation, this cookie does not require your consent.
		</div>
	</section>

	{% set matomoUrl = config('site-matomo-url') %}
	<section>
		<h2>Audience measurement (Matomo)</h2>
		<div class="text text-justify">
			This site may use Matomo, a self-hosted audience-measurement tool, to analyze its traffic. Configured according to the French data protection authority's (CNIL) exemption criteria (anonymized IP address, no cross-referencing with other sites, data kept for a maximum of 13 months, "Do Not Track" respected), its use likewise does not require your consent. It is only used for internal statistics, never for advertising purposes or resale to third parties.
			{% if matomoUrl %}
				You can still opt out at any time: <a href="{{ matomoUrl }}/index.php?module=CoreAdminHome&amp;action=optOut&amp;language=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">opt out of Matomo tracking</a>.
			{% endif %}
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Embedded third-party content</h2>
		<div class="text text-justify">
			Some pages may embed content hosted by a third-party site (a YouTube video, for example). This content sets its own cookies and requires your explicit consent, collected through the banner shown at the bottom of the page. Until you accept, this content is not loaded.
		</div>
	</section>

	<div>
		You can change your choice regarding third-party content at any time, or disable all cookies from your browser settings. For more information, and if you have any doubt or need clarification, please contact us.
	</div>
	<div>
		For further information about what French law says: <a href="https://www.cnil.fr/fr/cookies-et-autres-traceurs/que-dit-la-loi">https://www.cnil.fr/fr/cookies-et-autres-traceurs/que-dit-la-loi</a>
	</div>

	{% if config('site-other-cookies') %}
		<section>
			<h2>Other cookies</h2>
			<div class="text text-justify">
				{{ config('site-other-cookies')|raw|nl2br }}
			</div>
		</section>
	{% endif %}
</div>
